bench.gen

Class GenText

  • java.lang.Object
    • bench.gen.GenText
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenSegment

    public class GenText
extends java.lang.Object
implements GenSegment
    Holds xml template text in String format. This implementation of GenSegment holds text segments, i.e. any free text that is not part of a GenXml processing instruction.
    Version:
    TestHarness8.0
    Author:
    Progress Software Inc., all rights reserved.
